{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":760,"text":"Most of us go through life trying\nto do our best at whatever we do,"},{"time":4800,"text":"whether it's our job, family, school"},{"time":7400,"text":"or anything else."},{"time":9240,"text":"I feel that way. I try my best."},{"time":11920,"text":"But some time ago, I came to a realization"},{"time":14840,"text":"that I wasn't getting much better\nat the things I cared most about,"},{"time":18640,"text":"whether it was being a husband or a friend"},{"time":21840,"text":"or a professional or teammate,"},{"time":24080,"text":"and I wasn't improving\nmuch at those things"},{"time":26120,"text":"even though I was spending a lot of time"},{"time":28680,"text":"working hard at them."},{"time":31200,"text":"I've since realized from conversations\nI've had and from research"},{"time":34600,"text":"that this stagnation, despite hard work,"},{"time":37280,"text":"turns out to be pretty common."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39040,"text":"So I'd like to share with you\nsome insights into why that is"},{"time":41920,"text":"and what we can all do about it."},{"time":44160,"text":"What I've learned\nis that the most effective people"},{"time":46680,"text":"and teams in any domain"},{"time":48680,"text":"do something we can all emulate."},{"time":51000,"text":"They go through life deliberately\nalternating between two zones:"},{"time":55080,"text":"the learning zone\nand the performance zone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58160,"text":"The learning zone\nis when our goal is to improve."},{"time":60840,"text":"Then we do activities\ndesigned for improvement,"},{"time":63960,"text":"concentrating on what\nwe haven't mastered yet,"},{"time":66440,"text":"which means we have to expect\nto make mistakes,"},{"time":68920,"text":"knowing that we will learn from them."},{"time":71160,"text":"That is very different from what we do\nwhen we're in our performance zone,"},{"time":74920,"text":"which is when our goal is to do something\nas best as we can, to execute."},{"time":79240,"text":"Then we concentrate\non what we have already mastered"},{"time":81880,"text":"and we try to minimize mistakes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84840,"text":"Both of these zones\nshould be part of our lives,"},{"time":87280,"text":"but being clear about\nwhen we want to be in each of them,"},{"time":90560,"text":"with what goal, focus and expectations,"},{"time":92880,"text":"helps us better perform\nand better improve."},{"time":95720,"text":"The performance zone maximizes\nour immediate performance,"},{"time":98680,"text":"while the learning zone\nmaximizes our growth"},{"time":100800,"text":"and our future performance."},{"time":103320,"text":"The reason many of us don't improve much"},{"time":105400,"text":"despite our hard work"},{"time":107160,"text":"is that we tend to spend almost\nall of our time in the performance zone."},{"time":111880,"text":"This hinders our growth,"},{"time":113280,"text":"and ironically, over the long term,\nalso our performance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118040,"text":"So what does the learning zone look like?"},{"time":120760,"text":"Take Demosthenes, a political leader"},{"time":122800,"text":"and the greatest orator\nand lawyer in ancient Greece."},{"time":126240,"text":"To become great,\nhe didn't spend all his time"},{"time":129919,"text":"just being an orator or a lawyer,"},{"time":132360,"text":"which would be his performance zone."},{"time":134560,"text":"But instead, he did activities\ndesigned for improvement."},{"time":137600,"text":"Of course, he studied a lot."},{"time":139000,"text":"He studied law and philosophy\nwith guidance from mentors,"},{"time":141840,"text":"but he also realized that being a lawyer\ninvolved persuading other people,"},{"time":146400,"text":"so he also studied great speeches"},{"time":148800,"text":"and acting."},{"time":150640,"text":"To get rid of an odd habit he had\nof involuntarily lifting his shoulder,"},{"time":154960,"text":"he practiced his speeches\nin front of a mirror,"},{"time":157400,"text":"and he suspended a sword from the ceiling"},{"time":160400,"text":"so that if he raised his shoulder,"},{"time":162160,"text":"it would hurt."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":165040,"text":"To speak more clearly despite a lisp,"},{"time":167200,"text":"he went through his speeches\nwith stones in his mouth."},{"time":170840,"text":"He built an underground room"},{"time":172240,"text":"where he could practice\nwithout interruptions"},{"time":174400,"text":"and not disturb other people."},{"time":175840,"text":"And since courts at the time\nwere very noisy,"},{"time":178000,"text":"he also practiced by the ocean,"},{"time":179880,"text":"projecting his voice\nabove the roar of the waves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183400,"text":"His activities in the learning zone"},{"time":185120,"text":"were very different\nfrom his activities in court,"},{"time":187640,"text":"his performance zone."},{"time":189760,"text":"In the learning zone,"},{"time":191000,"text":"he did what Dr. Anders Ericsson\ncalls deliberate practice."},{"time":193800,"text":"This involves breaking down\nabilities into component skills,"},{"time":197360,"text":"being clear about what subskill\nwe're working to improve,"},{"time":200280,"text":"like keeping our shoulders down,"},{"time":202280,"text":"giving full concentration\nto a high level of challenge"},{"time":205160,"text":"outside our comfort zone,"},{"time":206600,"text":"just beyond what we can currently do,"},{"time":208960,"text":"using frequent feedback\nwith repetition and adjustments,"},{"time":212200,"text":"and ideally engaging the guidance\nof a skilled coach,"},{"time":215200,"text":"because activities\ndesigned for improvement"},{"time":217280,"text":"are domain-specific,"},{"time":218560,"text":"and great teachers and coaches\nknow what those activities are"},{"time":221480,"text":"and can also give us expert feedback."},{"time":223960,"text":"It is this type of practice\nin the learning zone"},{"time":226680,"text":"which leads to substantial improvement,"},{"time":228600,"text":"not just time on task performing."},{"time":231960,"text":"For example, research shows\nthat after the first couple of years"},{"time":235160,"text":"working in a profession,"},{"time":236440,"text":"performance usually plateaus."},{"time":238800,"text":"This has been shown to be true\nin teaching, general medicine,"},{"time":241880,"text":"nursing and other fields,"},{"time":243600,"text":"and it happens because once we think\nwe have become good enough,"},{"time":247360,"text":"adequate,"},{"time":248600,"text":"then we stop spending time\nin the learning zone."},{"time":250880,"text":"We focus all our time\non just doing our job,"},{"time":253080,"text":"performing,"},{"time":254320,"text":"which turns out not to be\na great way to improve."},{"time":257160,"text":"But the people who continue\nto spend time in the learning zone"},{"time":260120,"text":"do continue to always improve."},{"time":262280,"text":"The best salespeople at least once a week"},{"time":264720,"text":"do activities with\nthe goal of improvement."},{"time":267360,"text":"They read to extend their knowledge,"},{"time":269160,"text":"consult with colleagues or domain experts,"},{"time":271600,"text":"try out new strategies,\nsolicit feedback and reflect."},{"time":275360,"text":"The best chess players"},{"time":277000,"text":"spend a lot of time\nnot playing games of chess,"},{"time":280560,"text":"which would be their performance zone,"},{"time":282520,"text":"but trying to predict the moves\ngrand masters made and analyzing them."},{"time":286920,"text":"Each of us has probably spent\nmany, many, many hours"},{"time":291040,"text":"typing on a computer"},{"time":292600,"text":"without getting faster,"},{"time":294200,"text":"but if we spent 10 to 20 minutes each day"},{"time":297640,"text":"fully concentrating\non typing 10 to 20 percent faster"},{"time":300840,"text":"than our current reliable speed,"},{"time":302440,"text":"we would get faster,"},{"time":303720,"text":"especially if we also identified\nwhat mistakes we're making"},{"time":306760,"text":"and practiced typing those words."},{"time":309400,"text":"That's deliberate practice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312280,"text":"In what other parts of our lives,"},{"time":314040,"text":"perhaps that we care more about,"},{"time":315760,"text":"are we working hard but not improving much"},{"time":318320,"text":"because we're always\nin the performance zone?"},{"time":322560,"text":"Now, this is not to say\nthat the performance zone has no value."},{"time":325560,"text":"It very much does."},{"time":326800,"text":"When I needed a knee surgery,\nI didn't tell the surgeon,"},{"time":329480,"text":"\"Poke around in there\nand focus on what you don't know.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":332160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":333200,"text":"\"We'll learn from your mistakes!\""},{"time":335680,"text":"I looked for a surgeon\nwho I felt would do a good job,"},{"time":338960,"text":"and I wanted her to do a good job."},{"time":341160,"text":"Being in the performance zone"},{"time":342600,"text":"allows us to get things done\nas best as we can."},{"time":345800,"text":"It can also be motivating,"},{"time":347200,"text":"and it provides us with information\nto identify what to focus on next"},{"time":350800,"text":"when we go back to the learning zone."},{"time":353120,"text":"So the way to high performance"},{"time":354840,"text":"is to alternate between the learning zone\nand the performance zone,"},{"time":358560,"text":"purposefully building our skills\nin the learning zone,"},{"time":361120,"text":"then applying those skills\nin the performance zone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364560,"text":"When Beyoncé is on tour,"},{"time":366600,"text":"during the concert,\nshe's in her performance zone,"},{"time":369800,"text":"but every night when she\ngets back to the hotel room,"},{"time":372320,"text":"she goes right back\ninto her learning zone."},{"time":374560,"text":"She watches a video\nof the show that just ended."},{"time":377360,"text":"She identifies opportunities\nfor improvement,"},{"time":379520,"text":"for herself, her dancers\nand her camera staff."},{"time":382160,"text":"And the next morning,"},{"time":383440,"text":"everyone receives pages of notes\nwith what to adjust,"},{"time":386520,"text":"which they then work on during the day\nbefore the next performance."},{"time":390520,"text":"It's a spiral"},{"time":391760,"text":"to ever-increasing capabilities,"},{"time":393360,"text":"but we need to know when we seek to learn,\nand when we seek to perform,"},{"time":397000,"text":"and while we want\nto spend time doing both,"},{"time":399080,"text":"the more time we spend\nin the learning zone,"},{"time":401200,"text":"the more we'll improve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403360,"text":"So how can we spend\nmore time in the learning zone?"},{"time":407040,"text":"First, we must believe and understand"},{"time":410240,"text":"that we can improve,"},{"time":411600,"text":"what we call a growth mindset."},{"time":413840,"text":"Second, we must want\nto improve at that particular skill."},{"time":417120,"text":"There has to be a purpose we care about,"},{"time":419080,"text":"because it takes time and effort."},{"time":421360,"text":"Third, we must have an idea\nabout how to improve,"},{"time":424400,"text":"what we can do to improve,"},{"time":426120,"text":"not how I used to practice\nthe guitar as a teenager,"},{"time":428720,"text":"performing songs over and over again,"},{"time":430840,"text":"but doing deliberate practice."},{"time":432960,"text":"And fourth, we must be\nin a low-stakes situation,"},{"time":437160,"text":"because if mistakes are to be expected,"},{"time":439400,"text":"then the consequence of making them\nmust not be catastrophic,"},{"time":442440,"text":"or even very significant."},{"time":444240,"text":"A tightrope walker doesn't practice\nnew tricks without a net underneath,"},{"time":447960,"text":"and an athlete wouldn't set out\nto first try a new move"},{"time":450600,"text":"during a championship match."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453120,"text":"One reason that in our lives"},{"time":454800,"text":"we spend so much time\nin the performance zone"},{"time":457280,"text":"is that our environments\noften are, unnecessarily, high stakes."},{"time":462200,"text":"We create social risks for one another,"},{"time":464440,"text":"even in schools which are supposed\nto be all about learning,"},{"time":467320,"text":"and I'm not talking\nabout standardized tests."},{"time":469480,"text":"I mean that every minute of every day,"},{"time":471720,"text":"many students in elementary\nschools through colleges"},{"time":474440,"text":"feel that if they make a mistake,\nothers will think less of them."},{"time":477880,"text":"No wonder they're always stressed out"},{"time":479840,"text":"and not taking the risks\nnecessary for learning."},{"time":482760,"text":"But they learn\nthat mistakes are undesirable"},{"time":485040,"text":"inadvertently"},{"time":486320,"text":"when teachers or parents\nare eager to hear just correct answers"},{"time":489840,"text":"and reject mistakes\nrather than welcome and examine them"},{"time":492520,"text":"to learn from them,"},{"time":493800,"text":"or when we look for narrow responses"},{"time":495560,"text":"rather than encourage\nmore exploratory thinking"},{"time":497800,"text":"that we can all learn from."},{"time":499160,"text":"When all homework or student work\nhas a number or a letter on it,"},{"time":502280,"text":"and counts towards a final grade,"},{"time":504040,"text":"rather than being used for practice,\nmistakes, feedback and revision,"},{"time":507640,"text":"we send the message\nthat school is a performance zone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":512240,"text":"The same is true in our workplaces."},{"time":514320,"text":"In the companies I consult with,\nI often see flawless execution cultures"},{"time":518360,"text":"which leaders foster\nto encourage great work."},{"time":520960,"text":"But that leads employees\nto stay within what they know"},{"time":523520,"text":"and not try new things,"},{"time":524800,"text":"so companies struggle\nto innovate and improve,"},{"time":527160,"text":"and they fall behind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":529960,"text":"We can create more spaces for growth"},{"time":532280,"text":"by starting conversations with one another"},{"time":534360,"text":"about when we want to be in each zone."},{"time":537240,"text":"What do we want to get better at and how?"},{"time":539960,"text":"And when do we want\nto execute and minimize mistakes?"},{"time":543680,"text":"That way, we gain clarity\nabout what success is,"},{"time":546720,"text":"when, and how to best support one another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550000,"text":"But what if we find ourselves\nin a chronic high-stakes setting"},{"time":553120,"text":"and we feel we can't\nstart those conversations yet?"},{"time":556720,"text":"Then here are three things\nthat we can still do as individuals."},{"time":559840,"text":"First, we can create low-stakes islands\nin an otherwise high-stakes sea."},{"time":564640,"text":"These are spaces where mistakes\nhave little consequence."},{"time":567400,"text":"For example, we might find\na mentor or a trusted colleague"},{"time":570880,"text":"with whom we can exchange ideas\nor have vulnerable conversations"},{"time":574080,"text":"or even role-play."},{"time":575480,"text":"Or we can ask for feedback-oriented\nmeetings as projects progress."},{"time":579120,"text":"Or we can set aside time to read\nor watch videos or take online courses."},{"time":583280,"text":"Those are just some examples."},{"time":585360,"text":"Second, we can execute\nand perform as we're expected,"},{"time":589560,"text":"but then reflect on what\nwe could do better next time,"},{"time":592160,"text":"like Beyoncé does,"},{"time":593440,"text":"and we can observe and emulate experts."},{"time":595600,"text":"The observation, reflection\nand adjustment is a learning zone."},{"time":599880,"text":"And finally, we can lead"},{"time":602760,"text":"and lower the stakes for others\nby sharing what we want to get better at,"},{"time":606360,"text":"by asking questions\nabout what we don't know,"},{"time":608880,"text":"by soliciting feedback\nand by sharing our mistakes"},{"time":611400,"text":"and what we've learned from them,"},{"time":613040,"text":"so that others\ncan feel safe to do the same."}]},{"cues":[{"time":615760,"text":"Real confidence is about\nmodeling ongoing learning."},{"time":620880,"text":"What if, instead of spending\nour lives doing, doing, doing,"},{"time":625360,"text":"performing, performing, performing,"},{"time":627480,"text":"we spent more time exploring,"},{"time":630640,"text":"asking,"},{"time":632080,"text":"listening,"},{"time":633400,"text":"experimenting, reflecting,"},{"time":636520,"text":"striving and becoming?"},{"time":640320,"text":"What if we each always had something"},{"time":643160,"text":"we were working to improve?"},{"time":645760,"text":"What if we created more low-stakes islands"},{"time":648200,"text":"and waters?"},{"time":649840,"text":"And what if we got clear,"},{"time":652320,"text":"within ourselves and with our teammates,"},{"time":654720,"text":"about when we seek to learn\nand when we seek to perform,"},{"time":658280,"text":"so that our efforts\ncan become more consequential,"},{"time":661360,"text":"our improvement never-ending"},{"time":664040,"text":"and our best even better?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":667000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}